	CHARSET_ID_OFFSET_96 and final-byte.
	(LEADING_BYTE_LATIN_ISO8859_2): Likewise.
	(LEADING_BYTE_LATIN_ISO8859_3): Likewise.
	(LEADING_BYTE_LATIN_ISO8859_4): Likewise.
