	(MIN_LEADING_BYTE_PRIVATE_1): Changed from 0x0D0 to 0xD0.
	(MAX_LEADING_BYTE_PRIVATE_1): Changed from 0x11f to 0xDF.
	(CHARSET_ID_OFFSET_94x94): New macro.
