	`codesys->fixed.size' if TYPE is `no-conversion' and UTF2000 is
	defined.
	(encode_coding_no_conversion): New implementation for UTF2000.

	* file-coding.h (struct Lisp_Coding_System): Add new member
	`fixed.size'.

